CODE LAYOUT

 * Use 4 spaces per indentation level
 * Use spaces only (don't mix tabs, please)
 * All lines limited to a maximun of 80 characters
 * Encoding: UTF-8
 * Imports should be on separete lines
 * Avoid extraneous whitespaces inside parentheses, brackets or braces,
   before the open parentheses, immediately befora a comma, semicolon,
   or colon
 * Avoid more than one space around assignment operator to align it with
   another
 * Document everything
 * Add your name and email to AUTHORS and to any files you've edited

 Good Hacking
